==Tiwi==
===Noun===
'''purinjiti'''
# (''archaic'') A message stick used by news-bearers for [[safety]] when travelling into the [[territory|territories]] of other peoples.
'''Nota bene:''' The term '''purinjiti''' can be used in modern times for modern communication, i.e. the prescence of telephones, fax machines, [[&c]].

